`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
The per-chunk emitter Map pattern (`Map<chunkKey, ChunkEmitterSet>`) mirrors the existing `Map<string, Entity>` pattern in ChunkManager. The two-phase tick (stale cleanup first, then spawn/despawn per condition) keeps entity counts correct even when multiple chunks unload in one frame. The same pattern could extend to 4+ emitter types by just adding new fields to `ChunkEmitterSet`.
`─────────────────────────────────────────────────`

